 2002-09972002-06-110,  ,  ,  ,  ,  ,  CITIZENSHIP,  TB, 
PrecisEnactment of the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS which introduce measures to strengthen the refugee determination system, modernize the criteria for the selection of skilled workers and facilitate the admission of people in the family class, and, inter alia, establish, reinstate, raise or eliminate fees for various immigration services, and provide for the waiving of others, on an individual or class basis, and come into force on June 28, 2002.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2002-0227 Publication Date: 2002-07-03
